#String
##String Functions
### 1. Concatenation
#### using + operator
```
#include <iostream>
#include <string>

int main() {
    std::string str1 = "Hello, ";
    std::string str2 = "World!";
    std::string result = str1 + str2;
    std::cout << result << std::endl;  // Output: Hello, World!
    return 0;
}

```
